---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Άρθρα - Updated Layout" active="articles">

<main class="pt-32 pb-24 px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<!-- Hero Editorial Section -->
<header class="mb-20 text-center md:text-left max-w-3xl">
<span class="text-primary font-semibold tracking-widest text-xs uppercase mb-4 block">Editorial Journal</span>
<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-on-surface mb-8 leading-tight">
            Η Τέχνη της <span class="text-primary-container">Ευεξίας</span>
</h1>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xl leading-relaxed">
            Ανακαλύψτε επιστημονικά τεκμηριωμένες συμβουλές διατροφής, συνταγές και μυστικά για έναν πιο υγιή και ισορροπημένο τρόπο ζωής.
        </p>
</header>
<!-- Featured Bento Grid -->
<section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 mb-24">
<!-- Featured Article -->
<div class="md:col-span-8 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-2">
<div class="relative h-[500px] w-full overflow-hidden rounded-lg">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" data-alt="Modern wooden bowl filled with vibrant fresh salad ingredients, avocado, and seeds on a rustic linen cloth with soft sunlight" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDMLCxmNSmknn5M0qx9-HZhn3gdYyoNdWiC8uDdVTc8wZktvcLUFWc3Rp-FCKmxpkFTgk-Hl5sJFxRnVQOgaTWAMMtdLOln1K_dbKIQW6cM1hYZCBujIkjf2v3GYE6vbYipcr-WGC8jTnjOUK9fNB3PEFXNKCGPBfa3Xv_tYVJ3cOZfXER5W6-dQtXMwzJ4RjCqZc_t5mWhrzHIQS6BOcw0oK06uRHi834BHwT7AvxjWNKrM-ZRcjdTuv1Iv6qz6xj-RVObbcxE4B8"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-10 text-white">
<span class="bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold mb-4 inline-block">TRENDING</span>
<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Πώς η Μεσογειακή Διατροφή ενισχύει τη μακροζωία</h2>
<p class="text-emerald-50/80 mb-6 max-w-lg">Μια βαθιά ανάλυση στις διατροφικές συνήθειες των "Μπλε Ζωνών" και πώς να τις εφαρμόσετε σήμερα.</p>
<a class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white text-primary px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors" href="#">
                        Διαβάστε Περισσότερα
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Secondary Featured Stack -->
<div class="md:col-span-4 flex flex-col gap-8">
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-outline-variant/10">
<span class="text-primary font-bold text-xs mb-2 block">ΔΙΑΤΡΟΦΗ</span>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 leading-snug">5 Μύθοι για τους υδατάνθρακες που πρέπει να σταματήσετε να πιστεύετε</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-4">Γιατί η αποφυγή τους μπορεί να βλάψει τον μεταβολισμό σας.</p>
<a class="text-primary font-bold text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-1 hover:underline" href="#">
                    Περισσότερα <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">open_in_new</span>
</a>
</div>
<div class="bg-primary-container p-8 rounded-xl text-on-primary-container flex-grow flex flex-col justify-end">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl mb-4" data-weight="fill">cooking</span>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Εποχιακό Ημερολόγιο: Τι να τρώτε τον Απρίλιο</h3>
<p class="opacity-90 mb-6">Ο απόλυτος οδηγός για φρέσκα φρούτα και λαχανικά του μήνα.</p>
<a class="bg-on-primary-container text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-center font-bold text-sm" href="#">Δείτε τον Οδηγό</a>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Article Filters -->
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-12 items-center">
<span class="text-on-surface-variant font-semibold text-sm">Κατηγορίες:</span>
<button class="bg-primary text-on-primary px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Όλα</button>
<button class="bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium hover:bg-surface-container-highest transition-colors">Συνταγές</button>
<button class="bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium hover:bg-surface-container-highest transition-colors">Superfoods</button>
<button class="bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium hover:bg-surface-container-highest transition-colors">Vegan</button>
<button class="bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium hover:bg-surface-container-highest transition-colors">Ψυχολογία</button>
</div>
<!-- Article List Grid -->
<section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
<!-- Article 1 -->
<article class="flex flex-col">
<div class="relative aspect-video mb-6 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-surface-container">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-105" data-alt="Artisanal glass jars of overnight oats topped with fresh berries, almonds, and honey on a bright kitchen counter" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBmvc0VXZnKu5EErZo3_apN5lQnMe_7k1t6GL_tMSdM1oH4a61eFziG0MjrM_ZSdga--mJqX9ea_9gGnVUqFXTkc6sQ5-gXbxZe3f6Le6zf9Uf0ozFlthpE2JDye3EfDQ8F3r2SCEe5kO3Igor9wp34xqlE_UTd0HNLm7l_LaJeF_VXcdQVJ-bwVeSobiE89_9pzJXMb40OigumKS61mSPr6DHOw2A8Lsrr-M8s2jwu89N8xmLyJfxhaejoRvxLq3gBbzOxeEsAJWQ"/>
<span class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Συνταγές</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 leading-tight">Overnight Oats: Το ιδανικό πρωινό για ενέργεια</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-6 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
                3 εύκολες συνταγές που προετοιμάζονται από το προηγούμενο βράδυ για να ξεκινήσετε τη μέρα σας σωστά.
            </p>
<a class="inline-flex items-center text-primary font-bold hover:gap-3 transition-all" href="#">
                Διαβάστε Περισσότερα
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined ml-2 text-lg">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
</article>
<!-- Article 2 -->
<article class="flex flex-col">
<div class="relative aspect-video mb-6 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-surface-container">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-105" data-alt="Close-up of a colorful Buddha bowl with quinoa, roasted sweet potatoes, kale, and chickpeas in a ceramic bowl" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDyb3TDD6EpQUrJj4V-nJpAVLlCsywof3tmv3VPCBOWn08FMhUvfCLSpBdrAovJ4LrP7LGPj_X0hiFk0RV2W0ESCITtH_-gacX4u-bdOF57SoX3AQd2pfzu4gJEkGC_zb7eDMGN9NmItLsaweGsypOT83vrqpbtzP_i5rujhV55YmCDXOx1kc4E0m96gT-dzxoBvIfwalAXpoLKSkgCGqrAhqPKdMIuou9KQWeQEV5kX8S0dqAYvkWBA4FSjAsALtJ9X85aEJtD4qU"/>
<span class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Vegan</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 leading-tight">Η δύναμη της φυτικής πρωτεΐνης</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-6 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
                Μάθετε πώς να καλύπτετε τις ανάγκες σας σε πρωτεΐνη ακολουθώντας μια αποκλειστικά χορτοφαγική διατροφή.
            </p>
<a class="inline-flex items-center text-primary font-bold hover:gap-3 transition-all" href="#">
                Διαβάστε Περισσότερα
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined ml-2 text-lg">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
</article>
<!-- Article 3 -->
<article class="flex flex-col">
<div class="relative aspect-video mb-6 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-surface-container">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-105" data-alt="A person drinking fresh green cold-pressed juice from a glass bottle in a bright minimalist room" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuB0F_ckH-Zy_l5o7EkT4rEgnF7CPwPbG0qRg5RE7x7wgrqysPkQ6g8eep5toirwUgzMJa9uOB_mJHxDQXn5Inf3mypzB2F04kxVhA_TAoHKzB1yXdR46NnEvIuBQCrJPnkADJciBcRgVOGTJKib9USBE2hB-4KJdORRLU_cm4pS0xZvIbSfc7RjROFHneUuE5eKQjllWY-l5VhoY78RGcNho05jNrpRKPnXO-a8q_so71BiyzawphwO6GirN1z6sDZkpXhj45J5AXs"/>
<span class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Superfoods</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 leading-tight">Detox: Μύθος ή πραγματικότητα;</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-6 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
                Όλη η αλήθεια για τα προγράμματα αποτοξίνωσης και πώς το σώμα μας καθαρίζει φυσικά τον εαυτό του.
            </p>
<a class="inline-flex items-center text-primary font-bold hover:gap-3 transition-all" href="#">
                Διαβάστε Περισσότερα
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined ml-2 text-lg">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
</article>
<!-- Article 4 -->
<article class="flex flex-col">
<div class="relative aspect-video mb-6 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-surface-container">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-105" data-alt="Peaceful morning light hitting a yoga mat and a glass of lemon water on a wooden floor" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDQ-mex8_BbpnJPxPjaQrjQqHnPsPNIDOIPoe8Hf_s6tcqMX0-3CYWzP_7y4KF54mbmQdZ8nA3asgNVn2EcgFVsOrtlMAm8CisC7obsT2bz9sOKjSMFHqmLeFBT6SdO9o0vMr1pcqhtibhnoLtjO4bdJ-K2VH6ptnIr0ch0unSaNfF7gBK8oNQVs91oAGEN7uz-eJhWvQmf47GD-qDvvyT-V1yUvPgzThmmCbEBwb1FEIp6B8QOPCZRGbyIEfm-riwvn9rXvUJlQOk"/>
<span class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Ψυχολογία</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 leading-tight">Ενσυνείδητη Διατροφή (Mindful Eating)</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-6 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
                Πώς η προσοχή μας κατά τη διάρκεια του γεύματος μπορεί να αλλάξει τη σχέση μας με το φαγητό.
            </p>
<a class="inline-flex items-center text-primary font-bold hover:gap-3 transition-all" href="#">
                Διαβάστε Περισσότερα
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined ml-2 text-lg">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
</article>
<!-- Article 5 -->
<article class="flex flex-col">
<div class="relative aspect-video mb-6 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-surface-container">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-105" data-alt="Flat lay of various spices, turmeric, ginger, and garlic in stone bowls on a dark textured background" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDzH_02HxBNl2kUzrkVYgUrmMJJYcUh3jgDLBlnX_A8oJvA_snGQVTHfojlX_JQ5e8Et1pSY-sbntYZKK97Wlw7yT1xbe3CUj5mxbklfwEk_iKh13-Wn2yFYuj1GIw4OshVRzbmVGyN7XJScJ9yZHJlV2-B9pzDIA7v77ef_2Jk1EW11NFbERN5BsgBnpxMySnou4f-_utdGam3nSVvsD8NwO-vbbMMLC3-yeyOYrkFVrS8amu8IzSsij92PSz62mkt5ltvVG4L8eo"/>
<span class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Διατροφή</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 leading-tight">Αντιφλεγμονώδη βότανα της φύσης</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-6 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
                Ανακαλύψτε πώς ο κουρκουμάς και το τζίντζερ μπορούν να γίνουν οι σύμμαχοί σας κατά των φλεγμονών.
            </p>
<a class="inline-flex items-center text-primary font-bold hover:gap-3 transition-all" href="#">
                Διαβάστε Περισσότερα
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined ml-2 text-lg">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
</article>
<!-- Article 6 -->
<article class="flex flex-col">
<div class="relative aspect-video mb-6 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-surface-container">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-105" data-alt="Close-up of a glass of fresh water with lemon slices and ice on a clean, sunlit surface" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCWaRZKNgCw0U3Ha4cpw9VlnOVCR-rmZv7FMRbpHTCRFQ4mDPPqXTxhwha6v6jq0phPjjatRU-sDp3gCbc4Pn0a4lHG9rH0ZZjaYsWKeWyAtfJjvIMhMUhQwg0tORc1fwJU-Ys0yFtDyCWty3TC4-XFTcK76HWEMuytMFEksNVkx3gmiIAj93xZsh05K5d6Nyfo3l4Mj3Ty4ao7SPFiyEzDS4iH1h9Wc8u5uzl1FFmgI5CIiF7rSAEgVfO3Jbn545s7YttUZSkrP38"/>
<span class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Ευεξία</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 leading-tight">Η Σημασία της Ενυδάτωσης</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-6 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
                Μάθετε γιατί το νερό είναι το πιο σημαντικό θρεπτικό συστατικό και πώς να πετύχετε τους στόχους ενυδάτωσης καθημερινά.
            </p>
<a class="inline-flex items-center text-primary font-bold hover:gap-3 transition-all" href="#">
                Διαβάστε Περισσότερα
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined ml-2 text-lg">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
</article>
</section>
<!-- Pagination -->
<div class="mt-20 flex justify-center items-center gap-4">
<button class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface-variant opacity-50 cursor-not-allowed">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">chevron_left</span>
</button>
<button class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary text-on-primary font-bold">1</button>
<button class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface hover:bg-surface-container-highest transition-colors font-bold">2</button>
<button class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface hover:bg-surface-container-highest transition-colors font-bold">3</button>
<button class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface hover:bg-surface-container-highest transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">chevron_right</span>
</button>
</div>
</main>
</Layout>
